---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: Latest news and updates from Bellevue ARC
---

<div class="container">
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    <p>Stay up to date with the latest news and stories from Bellevue ARC.</p>
    
    <div class="blog-posts">
        {% for post in collections.blog %}
            <article class="blog-post-preview">
                <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
                <div class="post-meta">
                    <time datetime="{{ post.date | date('YYYY-MM-DD') }}">
                        {{ post.date | date('MMMM DD, YYYY') }}
                    </time>
                </div>
                {% if post.data.excerpt %}
                    <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
                {% endif %}
                <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read more â†’</a>
            </article>
        {% endfor %}
        
        {% if collections.blog.length == 0 %}
            <p>No blog posts yet. Check back soon!</p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
</div>